features: Compatible with all major U.S. carriers, including Verizon, AT&T, and T-Mobile. It also works with prepaid carriers, including Cricket Wireless, Metro by T-Mobile, Simple Mobile, Total Wireless, Tracfone, Net10, Mint, TracFone, and H2O.
Built-in Stylus. Jot notes, edit photos, sketch artwork, and navigate effortessly. Be more productive and unleash your imagination.
Fast Performance + 5G speed. Connect at the fastest possible speeds with 5G powered by a Snapdragon 6 Gen 1 processor*.
6.6" 120Hz*** display and Dolby Atmos. Experience immersive entertainment on a large FHD+ display backed by multidimensional sound.
50MP camera system. Capture your sharpest, brightest photos even in the most challenging light with Ultra Pixel technology.
256GB storage**. Hold your everyday inspirations and still have plenty of room for your apps, photos, songs, and movies.
Unbelievable battery life. Never worry about recharging thanks to a 5000mAh battery.****

Disclaimers: *5G service plan and 5G network coverage required; available only in select areas; device not compatible with all 5G networks. Contact your service provider for details. **Available user storage is less due to many factors, including operating system, software and functions utilizing part of this capacity; may change with software updates.

Disclaimers II: ***Auto mode has a minimum device refresh rate of 60Hz and a maximum refresh rate of 120Hz; actual refresh rate may be less and will vary based on app/content limitations and requirements, device mode settings, and other factors. ****Battery life claims approximate & based on median user tested across mixed use profile (includes both usage & standby time) under optimal network conditions. Actual battery performance will vary & depends on signal strength, network & device settings, temp, battery condition & usage patterns.
